@startuml
title Simple Shop System - Checkout Timing

robust "Customer" as C
robust "Web App" as W
concise "Order Service" as O
concise "Payment" as P

@0
C is Browsing
W is Idle
O is Idle
P is Idle

@100
C is Checkout
W is Submitting

@200
O is Validating

@300
O is Authorizing
P is Processing

@400
P is Approved
O is Confirmed
W is Success
C is Done
@enduml
